title: For Sale:  Sig Sauer P290RS Two-tone w/Night Sights +extras
location: Saint Paul (Midway), Minneapolis / St. Paul, Minnesota
postcontent:
Selling my Sig P290RS. Bought it for a deep concealment gun which it is excellent for but just don't find myself carrying it too much so I'll let it go for my asking price. Has factory Siglite tritium night sights. Wonderful shooter once you get used to the double action only trigger. Extremely accurate and very soft shooting for a small gun. Trigger feels about 8-9lbs but is very crisp. So far it has 400 flawless rounds through it (I guess that's a break in) Cleaned after every range trip.
